<problem id="fs-id1693881"><para id="fs-id2117718">Which of the following codes describes position 12 on the long arm of chromosome 13?</para>
<list id="fs-id1627623" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>13p12</item>
<item>13q12</item>
<item>12p13</item>
<item>12q13</item>
