<exercise id="fs-id1803123">
<problem id="fs-id1290311"><para id="fs-id2348913">In agriculture, polyploid crops (like coffee, strawberries, or bananas) tend to produce ________.</para>
<list id="fs-id1290266" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item>more uniformity</item>
<item>more variety</item>
<item>larger yields</item>
